➜【星连文学社】维港泊人（香港）：《七夕》
http://www.sohu.com/a/414806874_100115135	25438
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200825/1472463248bf41f2b758ff3f8a77b713.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>《七夕》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/维港泊人（香港）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">又见七夕</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">牛郎织女鹊桥会</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">仙凡配</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">相思凝固桥墩</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">思念铺筑桥面</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">滔滔银河，又多了几顷断肠泪</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">今夕何夕</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">天上人间</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">都羡美满姻缘</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">何苦你诈我骗</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">若真爱，莫让女子暗悲泣</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">堪称男儿有承担</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>（25，08，2020）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200825/10576c671bb642df93cb039f7cd4124a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
