➜【星连文学社】青衣小生：《祭月》-中秋（二）
http://www.sohu.com/a/414809765_100115135	26640
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200825/50741a1f14214164964f27d07b0c7c54.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>一《祭月》-中秋</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">秋分祭月夜迎寒，月闻笙箫水云间。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">举杯共饮游天外，莫笑屋漏农家酸。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200825/513968943e0a4099b81c9fe4557bed84.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>二《祭月》-中秋</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">夜逢佳节玉兔圆，嫦娥奔月苦霜寒。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">小饼如月连宵戏，笙箫随君诗意暖。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">举灯高燃望秋色，灯火不知世间难。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">小酌杯酒知深意，皓月凌空独自怜。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200825/c5db4612c3284d9fbfc09f853faaa9d2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
