➜【星连文学社】湖北诗人木子：七夕和我没关系
http://www.sohu.com/a/414821823_100115135	29453
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200825/623b69b140544d9580fb7a38c413656c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七夕和我没关系</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/木子</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">相依</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">相伴</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">吟诗作句</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">平平仄仄的韵律谱写着红尘中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">苦与乐 悲与喜</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一字一句</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">雕刻出日常碎念中的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一份惬意</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一份诗意</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所有的一切替代不了你的痕迹</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">灵魂溢香</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">无与伦比</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">温馨在心底</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我和七夕没关系</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>虚幻敌不过现实</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>过不去的河</strong></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
